name: PancakeTools
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Pancaketools binance chain pair and pool explorer based on data form PancakeSwap.
Pancaketools launch 20 May 2021 and will offer : 
- Pair&Pool explorer
- Calendar with upcoming listing in PancakeSwap
- Rating upcoming listing in PancakeSwap
- Staking
